how to keep cats out of windows to make a long story short i got an eviction notice to remove my cats from my apartment a neighbor told on me is there anyway i can keep the cats from jumping up in my front windows which face everyone elses apartment and just keep them to the back windows i dont want to get rid of my kitties and this is the only solution i can think of thanks try rubbing orange peels on the windows or spraying citrus air freshener near the windows cats hate citrus things Orange (fruit) Citrus Garfield The Inside Rent (musical) Blood Simple Essential oil The Dalek Invasion of Earth Cat Sin City Felis sapiens Taikyoku shogi Saki Shaggy dog story Great Teacher Onizuka Kitty Genovese The Subtle Knife Big Brother (USA TV series) Lime (fruit) Stop Huntingdon Animal Cruelty The Amber Spyglass Perfume Inland Empire (California) Quake III Arena Animal Liberation Front One Tree Hill (TV series) Friends Dai dai shogi Jam (TV series) Maneki Neko Volleyball Miss Saigon Bulldozer Vinegar Avenue Q Dai shogi GunZ The Duel Tai shogi Married... with Children Knight Rider Apple Fire fighting Alfred Hitchcock Cannabis cultivation The Cat in the Hat Reservoir Dogs Ultimate Spider-Man The Care Bears Adventure in Wonderland Richard Chase Citrus Park, Florida Marmalade The Demon Headmaster Rodney McKay Oh My Goddess! Piccolo Junior Saga Scarification Syphon Filter Linked list Skunk Maka dai dai shogi RuneScape quests Mutts The Parting of the Ways Aerial (dance move) Paul Gallico Propellerheads Tom and Jerry (MGM) Fullerton, California Do the Right Thing Girly Dodge Neon Phoebe Buffay The Invisibles Citrus canker Sega Dreamcast Lee Harvey Oswald Initiation: Silent Night, Deadly Night 4 W.I.T.C.H. Kakapo Riverside, California Austin Powers Angel One (TNG episode) Kitten Autonomous building Pottery Pinoy Big Brother Minor characters in Sonic the Hedgehog Sheikh Abdullah Glossary of ballet terms 2000 Australian Grand Prix Riot control B3ta Rear Window Night (book) GG Allin Conk